- Move the mouse cursor over a name to see more information.

- The arrows of the inheritance tree are

a.title: ― Identifier: Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.
a.xlink:title: ― Identifier: Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.

a.title: ― PairedControlledVocabularyEntry: A tightly bound pair of items from an external controlled vocabulary. The extent property describes the extent to which the parent term applies for the specific case.
a.xlink:title: ― PairedControlledVocabularyEntry: A tightly bound pair of items from an external controlled vocabulary. The extent property describes the extent to which the parent term applies for the specific case.

a.title: ― SpecializationRole: Specific roles played by represented variables in terms of time, geography, and other concepts which are important for the harmonization and integration of data.
a.xlink:title: ― SpecializationRole: Specific roles played by represented variables in terms of time, geography, and other concepts which are important for the harmonization and integration of data.

a.title: ― DataPoint: Container for an instance value.
a.xlink:title: ― DataPoint: Container for an instance value.

a.title: ― ForeignKeyComponent: Role of a data structure component for content referencing purposes
a.xlink:title: ― ForeignKeyComponent: Role of a data structure component for content referencing purposes

a.title: ― RepresentedVariable: Conceptual variable with a substantive value domain specified.
a.xlink:title: ― RepresentedVariable: Conceptual variable with a substantive value domain specified.

a.title: ― AttributeComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to qualify observations or provide other types of supplementary information.
a.xlink:title: ― AttributeComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to qualify observations or provide other types of supplementary information.

a.title: ― PrimaryKeyComponent: Role of a data structure component for content identification purposes
a.xlink:title: ― PrimaryKeyComponent: Role of a data structure component for content identification purposes

a.title: ― DataStructure: Data organization based on reusable data structure components.
a.xlink:title: ― DataStructure: Data organization based on reusable data structure components.

a.title: ― ComponentPosition: Indexes the components in a data structure using integers with a position indicated by incrementing upward from 0 or 1.
a.xlink:title: ― ComponentPosition: Indexes the components in a data structure using integers with a position indicated by incrementing upward from 0 or 1.

a.title: ― KeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a key.
a.xlink:title: ― KeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a key.

a.title: ― Member: Element in a collection that can be either atomic (individual member) or composite (collection).
a.xlink:title: ― Member: Element in a collection that can be either atomic (individual member) or composite (collection).

a.title: ― KeyValueStructure: Structure of a key-value datastore (organized collection of key-value data). It is described by identifier, contextual, synthetic id, dimension, variable descriptor and variable value components.
a.xlink:title: ― KeyValueStructure: Structure of a key-value datastore (organized collection of key-value data). It is described by identifier, contextual, synthetic id, dimension, variable descriptor and variable value components.

a.title: ― DimensionalDataStructure: Structure of a dimensional data set (organized collection of multidimensional data). It is described by dimension, measure and attribute components.
a.xlink:title: ― DimensionalDataStructure: Structure of a dimensional data set (organized collection of multidimensional data). It is described by dimension, measure and attribute components.

a.title: ― MeasureComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to hold the observed/derived values.
a.xlink:title: ― MeasureComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to hold the observed/derived values.

a.title: ― DimensionComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a dimensional data structure to identify the universes associated with data points. The variable acts as a field in the compound identifier (the key structure) to disambiguate the cells in the multi-dimensional "cube".
a.xlink:title: ― DimensionComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a dimensional data structure to identify the universes associated with data points. The variable acts as a field in the compound identifier (the key structure) to disambiguate the cells in the multi-dimensional "cube".

a.title: ― WideDataStructure: Structure of a wide dataset (organized collection of wide data). It is described by identifier, measure and attribute components.
a.xlink:title: ― WideDataStructure: Structure of a wide dataset (organized collection of wide data). It is described by identifier, measure and attribute components.

a.title: ― ContextualComponent: Encapsulates contextual information of the key-value datastore to provide a scope to the instance key. The instance key is unique within the scope.
a.xlink:title: ― ContextualComponent: Encapsulates contextual information of the key-value datastore to provide a scope to the instance key. The instance key is unique within the scope.

a.title: ― IdentifierComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a long or wide data structure to identify the units associated to data points, and in dimensional and key value data structures to provide identifying fields for the instance values.
a.xlink:title: ― IdentifierComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a long or wide data structure to identify the units associated to data points, and in dimensional and key value data structures to provide identifying fields for the instance values.

a.title: ― VariableDescriptorComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to provide codes for variable identification.
a.xlink:title: ― VariableDescriptorComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to provide codes for variable identification.

a.title: ― QualifiedMeasure: A measure having a specific production method.
a.xlink:title: ― QualifiedMeasure: A measure having a specific production method.

a.title: ― SyntheticIdComponent: Persistent and unique identifier (PIDs) to provide standarized, long-lasting identification.
a.xlink:title: ― SyntheticIdComponent: Persistent and unique identifier (PIDs) to provide standarized, long-lasting identification.

a.title: ― VariableValueComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to record values of multiple variables.
a.xlink:title: ― VariableValueComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to record values of multiple variables.

a.title: ― LongDataStructure: Structure of a long dataset (organized collection of long data). It is described by identifier, measure, attribute, variable descriptor and variable value components.
a.xlink:title: ― LongDataStructure: Structure of a long dataset (organized collection of long data). It is described by identifier, measure, attribute, variable descriptor and variable value components.

a.title: ― isDefinedBy: Data structure component is defined by zero to one represented variable.
a.xlink:title: ― isDefinedBy: Data structure component is defined by zero to one represented variable.
